<p>System: block</p>
<img src="/static/problems/S13/solutions/images/8-3(2).png" />

<p>\(\Sigma\) \(\vec{F}\) = m\(\vec{a}\) \(\Rightarrow\)  Mg - T = M\(\vec{a}\)    (1)</p>
<p></p>
<p>System: pulley</p>
<p>\(\sum \vec{\tau}_{cm}\) = - rT \(\hat{k}\) = - I<sub>cm</sub> \(\alpha\) \(\hat{k}\)</p>
<p>\(\alpha\) = \({rT\over I_{cm}}\)   (2) </p>
<p>The rope does not slide relative to pulley \(\Rightarrow\) a=\(\alpha\)r   (3)</p>
<p>use (3) and (1) in (2)  </p>
<p>\(\alpha\) = \({r\over I_{cm}}\)(Mg - Ma) = \({r\over I_{cm}}\) (Mg-M\(\alpha\)r)</p>
<p>\(\alpha\) = Mg\({r\over I_{cm}}\) - \({Mr^{2}\over I_{cm}}\)\(\alpha\)</p>
<p>\(\alpha\)(1 + \({Mr^{2}\over I_{cm}}\)) = \({Mgr\over I_{cm}}\)</p>
<p>\(\alpha\) = \({2g\over 3r}\)</p>
<p>Disc: I<sub>cm</sub> = \({Mr^{2}\over 2}\)</p>
<p>\(\alpha\) = \({{Mgr\over I_{cm}}\over 1+ {Mr^{2}\over I_{cm}}}\) = \({{2g\over r}\over 1 + 2}\) = \({2g\over 3r}\)</p>

</problem>
